    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1880-07-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1880-07-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="187" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d187">
                <head>No. 187.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <persName type="from">Chen Lan Pin and
                                    Mr. Yung Wing</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Evarts</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chinese
                                        Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1880-07-31">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 31,
                                1880</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: We have the honor to inclose herewith
                            copies of a note dispatched some time since by the Tsung-li Yamên at
                            Peking (the foreign office) to the ministers of China in foreign
                                countries.<note n="*" xml:id="d187fn1">See appendix 6 to Mr.
                                Seward’s No. 510 of Nov. 21, 1879, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_177">page 177</ref>.</note> We were instructed by
                            our government to communicate its contents to your excellency, and we
                            have caused an English translation of the note to be printed, to
                            facilitate its examination.</p>
                <p>Accept, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>CHEN LAN PIN.</item>
                            <item>YUNG WING.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
